<p>Lots of things have changed in the world of social media since the last release. To bring Hydejack up to date, the default logo for Twitter has changed:</p>

<p><span class="twitter-icon"></span> → <span class="x-icon"></span></p>

<p class="note">If you prefer the old Twitter logo, you can use it through <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">twitter-old</code>.</p>

